{
  "rewrites": [
    {
      "source": "/(.*)",
      "destination": "/frontend.jsx"
    }
  ]
}
```

**Step 5:** Click **"Commit changes"**

**Step 6:** Now Vercel will automatically redeploy. Wait 2-3 minutes.

